title: STAR LYRICS – B Jay Randhawa, SukhE | Punjabi Song
text:
by lyricsmint · March 22, 2017 Star Lyrics: A Punjabi song sung by B Jay Randhawa and Sukhe, music produced by Sukhe Muzical Doctorz while lyrics are penned by Jaani. STAR (Full Video) B Jay Randhawa Ft. Sukhe | Jaani | Monica Gill | Arvindr Khaira | New Songs 2017 
“Jatt Ta Star Hogaya” music video is directed by Arvindr Khaira starring B Jay Randhawa, SukhE and Monica Gill. Star Lyrics 
Tu mere dil naal dil fit karta Ni tu raaton raati munda hit karta (x2)
